## Request DTO Annotations

```go
type Item struct {
    ID          uint64 `json:",omitempty" example:"1"`
    Title       string `example:"Sample Title" validate:"required,min=2,max=255"`
    Description string `example:"Sample description"`
    Price       uint64 `example:"10000" validate:"required,number"`
    Status      string `example:"active" validate:"required,oneof=active inactive"`
}
```

## Generating Swagger Docs

```bash
# Install swag CLI
go install github.com/swaggo/swag/cmd/swag@latest

# Generate docs
swag init -g cmd/main/main.go -o docs

# With specific parse depth
swag init -g cmd/main/main.go -o docs --parseDepth 1
```

